      <url>2021/02/18/Spring-vs-Spring-Boot/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spring</strong> is the most popular application development framework of Java. The main features of the Spring Framework are Dependency Injection (DI) / Inversion of Control (IoC), and Aspect Oriented Programming (AOP).</p><p><strong>Spring MVC</strong> is a model view controller-based web framework under the Spring framework.</p><p><strong>Spring Boot</strong> is a module of Spring for packaging the Spring-based application with sensible defaults. It allows us to build a stand-alone application with minimal or zero configurations.</p>]]></content>
      
      
