      <title>Prevent Browsers from cacheing JS/CSS</title>
      <link href="2020/03/15/Prevent-Browsers-from-cacheing-JS-CSS/"/>
      <url>2020/03/15/Prevent-Browsers-from-cacheing-JS-CSS/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Browsers always cache js/css files, and then the updates won’t take effect immediately after new production release.</p><p>Add session id into js/css loading to prevent the caching.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;script.js?session&#x3D;&lt;%&#x3D;&#x2F;&#x2F;code to get the session ID %&gt;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
