      <title>Hexo admin setup</title>
      <link href="2020/03/13/Hexo-admin/"/>
      <url>2020/03/13/Hexo-admin/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Instead of using command to publish hexo post, Hexo admin plugin provide a GUI interface.</p><p>For installation, refer to <a href="https://github.com/jaredly/hexo-admin">this</a>.</p><p>After installation, setup deploymentCommand in admin.</p><ol><li><p>create sh file in the hexo root directory</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi hexo-pubish.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Write commands and save in sh file</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!&#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;env sh</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Modify the execution permission of the sh file</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x hexo-publish.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Modify configuration file by adding deployCommand setting </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># hexo-admin authentification</span><br><span class="line">admin:</span><br><span class="line">  username: ******</span><br><span class="line">  password_hash: ******</span><br><span class="line">  secret: ******</span><br><span class="line">  deployCommand: &#39;.&#x2F;hexo-publish.sh&#39;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
